   <span style="font-weight:bold">Obama hit often by McCain negative ads</span>
   <p></p>
  </div>
  <br />
  <div>
   Classified as: 1
  </div>Article written on :2008-08-07
  <p class="c8"><span class="c2">The presidential campaign is in full swing, and Sen. John McCain seems to be enjoying himself with negative ads on TV about Sen. Barack Obama. We see new ads almost daily in Obama negativity.</span></p> 
  <p class="c8"><span class="c2">There is one line in an ad that Obama could use that would stop McCain in his tracks. And that one line is: &quot;A vote for McCain would be insane!&quot;</span></p> 
  <p class="c8"><span class="c2">Roger Bomberger</span></p> 
  <p class="c8"><span class="c2">Lebanon </span></p>
